name: A Night At The Barn
description:
A cozy night at the barn. Sharo, the shepherd's dog is looking after the sheep. This piece is part of Vegzi's Hiragana Art World. Collectors from primary market get a special NFT #23 from Vegzi's Hiragana Collection.
Medium: 1080x1080 MP4 with sound / Animated illustration loop / Artist: Vegzi / Twitter: @Vegzi1 / Created and minted: 10th of July 2021
